name: Corporal Drelosyn
Lore: 'Stormtrooper from Coruscant. Honed piloting skills by racing swoops in underworld of Imperial capital. Still tempering his skills as a biker scout.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots or anything he drives. When in battle with Irol at a site, adds one battle destiny. Power +1 at any mobile, interior or spaceport site.',
